text: The corpus spongiosum is the mass of spongy tissue surrounding the male urethra within the penis. It is also called the corpus cavernosum urethrae in older texts. ==Related pages== * Corpus cavernosum penis * Spongy urethra * Trabeculae of corpus spongiosum of penis ==References== ==Other websites== * - "The Male Pelvis: The Urethra" Category:Penis
title: Corpus spongiosum (penis)
